Class ImageTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
      • com.epam.finaltask.tag.ImageTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ImageTag
extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
    Jsp tag class, Can be used to create tag which shows chosen image if condition is met, and default image if it isn't.

    • Method Detail

      • doStartTag

        public int doStartTag()
               throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspException
        Generates html to display image. If test is true, then image specified in src will be displayed. Otherwise defaultSrc image will be used. Width and height can be specified using width and height. Style if the img tag can be specified using imgClass. alt content is passed to alt attribute of the img html tag.
        Specified by:
        doStartTag in interface javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
        Overrides:
        doStartTag in class javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
        Returns:
        SKIP_BODY constant.
        Throws:
        javax.servlet.jsp.JspException - if IOException will be thrown by JspWriter
